beer.beer_description:
Tai pagal klasikin? škotiško elio technologij? išvirtas "Švyturio Old Port ale" (5,6 %) alus. D?l ilgesnio virimo proceso, karamelinio salyklo ir žemos fermentacijos temperat?ros jis apdovanotas tamsiai raudona rubino spalva, karameliniu skoniu, salykliniu aromatu bei tvirta puta. Tinka su ispaniškais kumpiais, avienos patiekalais.

It is based on the classical technology Scotch Eli cooked Švyturys Old Port Ale (5.6%) beer. For longer cooking process, caramel malt and low fermentation temperature was awarded a dark red ruby ​​color, caramel flavor, malt flavor and a firm foam.
 
That special Old Port ale taste and aroma unfold even better, we combine it with Spanish ham or hot mutton dishes. 
 
Švyturys Old Port ale "- decorated in any Scottish pub!
